# Wizard Design – 1:1 Preservation

## CRITICAL
The wizard design MUST stay consistent (dark theme, Kotlin purple). Do not change:
- **Colors**: --kotlin-purple (#7f52ff), --kotlin-purple-hover (#9370ff), --wizard-bg (#1e1e1e), --wizard-bg-elevated (#252526), --wizard-border (#3d3d3d)
- **Font**: JetBrains Mono (font-mono)
- **Layout**: Two-column (config left, sidebar right), footer with GitHub link + Generate button
- **Option chips**: Inline radio-style chips with purple highlight when selected
- **Form fields**: Uppercase labels, bordered inputs, Kotlin purple focus ring

## Sections (in order)
1. Project (Single / Multi-Module)
2. Source Language (Kotlin / Java) + hint about Gradle .kts
3. Project Metadata (Name, Group)
4. Modules (API Module, Plugin Module) – hidden when Single
5. Java (17, 21, 25)
6. Versions (Kotlin, Paper API) – Kotlin hidden when Java selected
7. Publishing (GitHub Packages) – hidden when Single
